text: Zofia Kowalczyk (born 30 April 1929) is a Polish gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kraków
